These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, disco, hip-hop, techno
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, grey, ebony, brown
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the fan of salsa is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person who likes white is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre    | disco  | techno | hip-hop    | salsa       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| Color   | white   | ebony | grey | brown        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, march, october
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, gardening, singing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the musician is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is the fisherman##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Birthday        | march   | april | december     | october      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Hobby   | gardening    | woodworking   | singing     | writing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, siglo, montecristo, bongani
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
House: tower, colonial, cape-cod, gothic-revival
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the colonial house is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the bongani-smoker is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
7. the dunhill-smoker is the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Cigar         | dunhill | siglo | montecristo | bongani |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| House   | tower | cape-cod    | gothic-revival | colonial    |

