.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, bridge, mah-jongg
There are 4 different nationalities: british, spanish, turkish, canadian
1. the freelancer is the canadian##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
3. the turkish is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
6. the person playing monopoly is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Game       | scrabble     | mah-jongg      | monopoly     | bridge      |
| Nationality   | spanish | british         | canadian      | turkish        |

