.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, chinese, nigerian
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, lavender, brown
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, climbing, snowboarding
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
2. the chinese is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who likes lavender##1
5. the canadian is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the canadian is the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the nigerian is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Nationality         | chinese   | nigerian | german  | canadian      |
| Color   | lavender  | purple        | brown  | fuchsia       |
| Sport         | badminton | climbing    | biathlon | snowboarding |

