.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, malaysian, brazilian, canadian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bolivar, davidoff, oliveros
1. the accountant is the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the argentine is on the right of the writer##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the brazilian is the mechanic##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the malaysian##1
8. the writer is the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Nationality   | canadian   | brazilian  | malaysian | argentine   |
| Cigar   | oliveros   | chaman     | davidoff | bolivar       |

