.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, gospel, electronic, reggae
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, skydiving, video-games
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, may, january
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is the fan of electronic##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the fan of punk##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre          | punk  | reggae | electronic   | gospel     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking   | baking  | skydiving |
| Birthday   | may         | february  | december | january  |

