.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
House: cottage, cape-cod, tower, craftsman
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bongani, chaman, old-henry
1. the cape-cod house is the chaman-smoker##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is the tower house##1
7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
8. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| House      | craftsman | tower     | cottage | cape-cod |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Cigar   | bongani   | old-henry | vegafina    | chaman |

