.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite, rose, tulip
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, argentine, colombian, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, soccer, water-polo
1. the argentine is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the argentine is on the left of the colombian##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the dutch##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Flower          | rose        | tulip   | aconite  | orchid   |
| Nationality   | brazilian         | dutch     | argentine    | colombian       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | lacrosse | soccer | water-polo |

