.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, november, september, may
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, camping, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | november    | september | may | january        |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks | baking  | cooking | camping     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

