.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
House: art-deco, victorian, cottage, wooden
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
4 different games are played: go, domino, canasta, chess
1. the person playing go is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the victorian house##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the person playing go is on the left of the wooden house##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the person playing canasta##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| House         | art-deco  | wooden | victorian  | cottage |
| Sport       | volleyball | rugby        | weightlifting | cricket       |
| Game   | go   | domino          | chess          | canasta       |

