.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, dancing, traveling
House: cottage, townhouse, farmhouse, craftsman
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, begonia, daisy
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the craftsman house is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling   | dancing   | card-games | cooking |
| House   | farmhouse | cottage | townhouse   | craftsman |
| Flower   | daisy     | zinnia  | begonia  | iris  |

