.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, reading, traveling
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, goldfish, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, trike, jet-ski, airplane
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| Pet   | snake     | goldfish     | lizard        | hedgehog   |
| Transport         | trike   | ship | jet-ski | airplane  |

