.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, mystery, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, metal, d&b, r&b
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, software-developer, scientist, entrepreneur
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the software-developer is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
8. the fan of metal is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | superhero  | comedy    | mystery    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | d&b  | jazz  | metal |
| Job     | entrepreneur  | software-developer | scientist | chef        |

