.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, artichoke, kale, asparagus
City: marseilles, hannover, new-york, liverpool
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating kale##1
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is the person eating asparagus##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person eating avocado is the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Food      | avocado        | asparagus    | artichoke | kale      |
| City   | marseilles        | liverpool   | hannover  | new-york  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball | soccer   | climbing |

