.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, artichoke, cranberry, orange
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, skiing, surfing, tennis
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating apple##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person eating artichoke is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | apple     | orange   | cranberry | artichoke |
| Sport   | sailing | tennis | surfing | skiing   |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate    | juice     | fanta      | milk     |

