4 different games are played: poker, monopoly, snooker, bridge
There 4 different types of food: radish, carrot, apple, potato
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, french, mexican
1. the person eating carrot is on the left of the french##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating radish is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person eating apple is the chinese##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the mexican##1
7. the french is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Game           | snooker  | poker | monopoly  | bridge |
| Food   | apple    | radish       | carrot | potato      |
| Nationality   | chinese | canadian  | mexican    | french    |

