.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indonesian, mexican, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, family, satire, drama
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite, lily, daffodil
1. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the british##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | british | indonesian | mexican | russian |
| Movie-Genre         | family | action | drama  | satire  |
| Flower     | zinnia  | aconite | daffodil     | lily  |

