.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: satired-games, trance, salsa, disco
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, chef, lawyer, nurse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, satire, epic, documentary
1. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the fan of disco is on the right of the chef##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
6. the fan of trance is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the fan of disco is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre       | satired-games | trance | disco | salsa |
| Job         | accountant | chef  | nurse   | lawyer      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire        | epic  | documentary   | time-travel         |

