.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, jet-ski, tram
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, pakistani, russian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, lemonade, milk
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Transport           | ship  | jet-ski  | bike | tram |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| Beverage         | water | lemonade    | 7up   | milk         |

 